{"data": [{"id": "4742801", "title": "Asana Stock Becomes An AI Play (Ratings Downgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/77481330/image_77481330.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Facebook Co-Founder Dustin Moskovitz Speaks At CTIA\" data-id=\"77481330\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"3504px\" height=\"2336px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/77481330/image_77481330.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/77481330/image_77481330.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/77481330/image_77481330.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/77481330/image_77481330.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/77481330/image_77481330.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/77481330/image_77481330.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/77481330/image_77481330.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/77481330/image_77481330.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Kimberly White</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Asana (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ASAN\" title=\"Asana, Inc.\">ASAN</a></span>) saw its stock pop to the tune of 40% after releasing earnings. While the company has yet to see top-line growth accelerate meaningfully, it did roll-out a new AI Studio product which appears to have analysts optimistic</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/77481330/image_77481330.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742801-asana-stock-becomes-ai-play-ratings-downgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 14:34:11"}, {"id": "4742799", "title": "Expect Another Excellent Year From Redwire, But Not Like Last Year", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1738898622/image_1738898622.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Two Astronauts On Tethered Spacewalk Facing Each Other\" data-id=\"1738898622\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"768px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1738898622/image_1738898622.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1738898622/image_1738898622.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1738898622/image_1738898622.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1738898622/image_1738898622.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1738898622/image_1738898622.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1738898622/image_1738898622.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1738898622/image_1738898622.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1738898622/image_1738898622.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">peepo</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Investment thesis</strong></h2> <p>The shares of Redwire Corporation (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RDW\" title=\"Redwire Corporation\">RDW</a></span>) have been on an astonishing journey over the past year. They had increased 409.78% by the close on December 6, 2024.</p> <p>In part, that increase is because of a bullish </p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1738898622/image_1738898622.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742799-expect-another-excellent-year-from-redwire-but-not-like-last-year", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 14:22:03"}, {"id": "4742800", "title": "Preparing Portfolios For Multi-Asset Opportunities Ahead Of 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961556676/image_961556676.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Mortgage concept by money house from the coins,Business Finance and Money concept,Saving money concept to buy a house.\" data-id=\"961556676\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961556676/image_961556676.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961556676/image_961556676.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961556676/image_961556676.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961556676/image_961556676.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961556676/image_961556676.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961556676/image_961556676.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961556676/image_961556676.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/961556676/image_9